      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Parade</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Be careful what you say </l>
          <l>about thses early days </l>
          <l>i think i'm loosing it. </l>
          <l>Girls in a parade </l>
          <l>fireworks in hell </l>
          <l>the dream is over soon. </l>
          <l>god if this was true </l>
          <l>i would have been so </l>
          <l>different and happy - you know. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>Sittuation's bad </l>
          <l>can not hold your head </l>
          <l>above the water. </l>
          <l>Girls, they come and go </l>
          <l>like fireworks and snow, it will be over soon </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>i wish i could film the things that i see </l>
          <l>when my eyes are closed </l>
          <l>every day's a dream </l>
          <l>nothing is 4 real </l>
          <l>open your eyes... </l>
          <l>....and now the parade is over </l>
          <l>you find yourself covered in mud </l>
          <l>and no one will show up tomorrow at work...</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
